This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The proposed approach involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves constructing a new dataset, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed approach in terms of security, which could also be categorized under cryptography and security (cs.CR).
